defs.name: Atom
defs.value: pub enum Atom { Num(i32), Keyword(String), Boolean(bool), BuiltIn(BuiltIn), }

defs.name: Expr
defs.value:
pub enum Expr {
    Constant(Atom),
    Application(Box<Expr>, Vec<Expr>),
    If(Box<Expr>, Box<Expr>),
    IfElse(Box<Expr>, Box<Expr>, Box<Expr>),
    Quote(Vec<Expr>),
}
